modName: Heels on platform CBBE ADEC UNP - DELETED
summary:
For CBBE 3.2, UNP, ADEC
24 variants of heels, 13 variants of stockings, requires HDT high heels
descriptionHtml:
It is returning of my old mod

24 variants of heels, 13 variants of stockings
Requires [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36213]HDT high heels[/url]
heels are following variants: black, bluefull , bluetop, cyanfull, cyantop,
dark green full, dark green top, dark purp full, dark purp top, dark red
full, dark red top, olive full, olive top, orange full, orange
top, pink full, pink top, red, red full, red top, silver, white full,
white top, yellow

stockings are following variants: transparent (black, cyan , olive, purple, red, white) net (black, blue, darkred,
green, orange, pink, white)

for model thanks to DonMichael71 [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/15982]High Heels for Modding[/url]
craftable in leather

This file is for CBBE 3.2 body, UNP and ADEC

File for CBBE 3.4f is [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/81269]here[/url]

Credits
for celtic brushes thanks to Falln-Stock  http://falln-stock.deviantart.com/art/Celtic-Knot-Brushes-92727098
